Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖...满了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠的愿望改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是契约是不能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就像是诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要去我该去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...

